premise_source_doc_sentence: SummerSlam  (  1992  )  was the fifth annual SummerSlam professional wrestling pay-per-view  (  PPV  )  event produced by the World Wrestling Federation  (  WWF  )  .
SummerSlam  (  2007  )  was the twentieth annual SummerSlam professional wrestling pay-per-view  (  PPV  )  event produced by World Wrestling Entertainment  (  WWE  )  .
SummerSlam is a professional wrestling pay-per-view  (  PPV  )  event , produced annually in August by professional wrestling promotion WWE .
SummerSlam  (  2011  )  was a professional wrestling pay-per-view  (  PPV  )  event produced by WWE that took place on August 14 , 2011 .
The inaugural SummerSlam took place on August 29 , 1988 at Madison Square Garden in New York City and was broadcast via pay-per-view .
